flowchart LR
  subgraph Client[Agent Client / CLI]
    A[Stable system prompt + tool schemas
(frozen bytes)]
    B[Dynamic messages
(chat history, tool results)]
    C[Out-of-band metadata
(telemetry, git status)]
  end

  subgraph Proxy[Cache-Aware Prompt Proxy]
    D[Validate stable prefix hash]
    E[Assemble request:
Stable prefix + Dynamic segment]
    F[Log metadata separately]
  end

  subgraph Backend[Local Inference Backend]
    G[Prefix/KV cache]
    H[Model inference]
  end

  A --> D --> E --> G --> H
  B --> E
  C --> F
  F -.not in prompt.-> H
